        {
            "title": "中船防務發盈喜 料首季純利升最多1.33倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中船防務(00317)發盈喜，預期今年首季實現歸屬母公司所有者淨利潤，將介乎3.6億至4.3億元(人民幣．下同)，按年升95.16%至1.33倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中船防務官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/00317-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中船防務官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/00317-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中船防務官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">估計期內扣除非經常性損益的歸母淨利潤，將介乎3.3億至3.9億元，按年也升85.44%至1.19倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司指出，期內盈利提升，主要因為公司把握船舶行業發展機遇，訂單承接態勢良好，產品結構不斷優化；持續深化精益生產管理，主建船型建造週期進一步壓降，推動營業收入穩步增長，產品毛利同比增加；另外，公司聯營企業經營業績顯著提升，確認投資收益大幅增加，亦有助盈利。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15869419-%e4%b8%ad%e8%88%b9%e9%98%b2%e5%8b%99%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e5%96%9c-%e6%96%99%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a1-33%e5%80%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20240709_FI_source-web_00317.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 08:27:47",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "喜相逢折讓16%配股籌1.52億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">喜相逢(02473)公布，擬配股集資約1.52億元；配股價0.98元，較該股昨天收市價1.16元折讓約16%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：喜相逢官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_FI_source-web_02473.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：喜相逢官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_FI_source-web_02473.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：喜相逢官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若與該股前5個交易日平均收市價1.13元比較，配股價則折讓約13%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">估計集資所得淨額約1.51億元，其中50%將用於購置與主營業務相關的機動車輛，包括為汽車零售及融資業務及汽車相關業務項下擬銷售或出租予客戶的車輛採購，以及為支持公司直接零售業務及海外業務拓展持續發展所需的車輛採購。該等資金預期將於12個月內悉數動用。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資淨額餘下約50%，將用作補充經營附屬公司的一般營運資金，以供一般企業用途，包括支持主營業務的日常營運及持續業務發展。該等資金預期將於12個月內悉數動用。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15869428-%e5%96%9c%e7%9b%b8%e9%80%a2%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9316%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c1-52%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/02473-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 08:27:47",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期夜期均高水逾250點 重磅港股ADR多半升過1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時15分升282點或1.1%，報25928點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報25900點，較香港上日現貨收市高239點或0.93%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣498.1元，較上日香港收市高8.07元或1.65%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣125.3元，較上日香港收市高2.09元或1.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣87.7元，較上日香港收市高1.28元或1.49%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣113.3元，較上日香港收市高1元或0.89%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣31.2元，較上日香港收市高0.5元或1.64%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣142.5元，較上日香港收市高3.68元或2.65%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣88.7元，較上日香港收市高1.26元或1.44%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣411元，較上日香港收市高5.2元或1.28%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣62.6元，較上日香港收市高0.91元或1.48%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.5元，較上日香港收市高0.03元或0.38%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報25924點，升259點，較上日恒指收市25660點，高水263點。科指期貨夜市收報4867點，較上日科指收市高水45點；國指期貨夜市收報8670點，較上日國指收市高水68點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15869458-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e5%9d%87%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be250%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e5%a4%9a%e5%8d%8a%e5%8d%87%e9%81%8e1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-14 08:22:22",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日韓股市初段顯著反彈 日股暫升逾千點 韓股漲超2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">隔晚華爾街股市造好，支撐日韓等亞洲主要股市今早初段顯著反彈。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241218_FI_source-ap_South_Korea_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241218_FI_source-ap_South_Korea_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時13分，日經平均指數報57565點，升1062點或1.88%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫升141點或2.43%，報5949點。</p>\n</div>",
